---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="en">

<head>

    <title>
        Privacy Policy | Passport Eligibility Checker
    </title>

    <meta
        name="description"
        content="Learn how Passport Eligibility Checker handles document processing, privacy, security and user information."
    />

</head>

<body class="bg-slate-50">

    <main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">

        <!-- Hero -->

        <section
            class="
                relative
                overflow-hidden
                py-24
                text-center
            "
        >

            <div
                class="
                    absolute
                    top-0
                    left-1/2
                    -translate-x-1/2
                    w-[500px]
                    h-[500px]
                    rounded-full
                    bg-blue-200/20
                    blur-3xl
                "
            ></div>

            <span
                class="
                    text-blue-600
                    font-semibold
                    uppercase
                    tracking-widest
                "
            >
                Privacy Policy
            </span>

            <h1
                class="
                    mt-4
                    text-5xl
                    font-bold
                    text-slate-900
                "
            >
                Your Privacy Matters
            </h1>

            <p
                class="
                    mt-6
                    text-xl
                    text-slate-600
                    max-w-3xl
                    mx-auto
                    leading-8
                "
            >
                We are committed to protecting
                your privacy and maintaining
                transparency about how document
                information is processed.
            </p>

        </section>

        <!-- Main Policy -->

        <section class="space-y-8">

            <div
                class="
                    bg-white
                    rounded-3xl
                    border
                    border-slate-200
                    p-10
                    shadow-sm
                "
            >

                <h2
                    class="
                        text-3xl
                        font-bold
                        text-slate-900
                    "
                >
                    Information Processing
                </h2>

                <p
                    class="
                        mt-6
                        text-slate-600
                        leading-8
                    "
                >
                    Passport Eligibility Checker
                    is designed to assist users in
                    reviewing document consistency
                    before passport-related
                    verification processes.
                </p>

                <p
                    class="
                        mt-4
                        text-slate-600
                        leading-8
                    "
                >
                    Uploaded documents may be
                    processed temporarily to
                    extract information such as
                    names, dates of birth and
                    document numbers required
                    for verification purposes.
                </p>

            </div>

            <!-- Local Processing -->

            <div
                class="
                    bg-white
                    rounded-3xl
                    border
                    border-slate-200
                    p-10
                    shadow-sm
                "
            >

                <h2
                    class="
                        text-3xl
                        font-bold
                        text-slate-900
                    "
                >
                    Local Document Processing
                </h2>

                <p
                    class="
                        mt-6
                        text-slate-600
                        leading-8
                    "
                >
                    Whenever possible, document
                    processing and OCR operations
                    are performed locally within
                    the user's browser environment.
                </p>

                <p
                    class="
                        mt-4
                        text-slate-600
                        leading-8
                    "
                >
                    This approach helps minimize
                    unnecessary exposure of
                    personal information and
                    gives users greater control
                    over their documents.
                </p>

            </div>

            <!-- Data Storage -->

            <div
                class="
                    bg-white
                    rounded-3xl
                    border
                    border-slate-200
                    p-10
                    shadow-sm
                "
            >

                <h2
                    class="
                        text-3xl
                        font-bold
                        text-slate-900
                    "
                >
                    Data Storage
                </h2>

                <p
                    class="
                        mt-6
                        text-slate-600
                        leading-8
                    "
                >
                    We do not intentionally
                    maintain a permanent database
                    of uploaded identity documents
                    for verification purposes.
                </p>

                <p
                    class="
                        mt-4
                        text-slate-600
                        leading-8
                    "
                >
                    Users should avoid uploading
                    documents on shared devices
                    and should review all
                    information before submission.
                </p>

            </div>

            <!-- Security -->

            <div
                class="
                    bg-white
                    rounded-3xl
                    border
                    border-slate-200
                    p-10
                    shadow-sm
                "
            >

                <h2
                    class="
                        text-3xl
                        font-bold
                        text-slate-900
                    "
                >
                    Security Measures
                </h2>

                <p
                    class="
                        mt-6
                        text-slate-600
                        leading-8
                    "
                >
                    We take reasonable measures
                    to provide a secure user
                    experience. However, no
                    online service can guarantee
                    absolute security.
                </p>

                <p
                    class="
                        mt-4
                        text-slate-600
                        leading-8
                    "
                >
                    Users remain responsible for
                    protecting their devices,
                    passwords and sensitive
                    personal information.
                </p>

            </div>

            <!-- User Responsibility -->

            <div
                class="
                    bg-white
                    rounded-3xl
                    border
                    border-slate-200
                    p-10
                    shadow-sm
                "
            >

                <h2
                    class="
                        text-3xl
                        font-bold
                        text-slate-900
                    "
                >
                    User Responsibility
                </h2>

                <p
                    class="
                        mt-6
                        text-slate-600
                        leading-8
                    "
                >
                    Verification results generated
                    by this tool are provided for
                    informational purposes only.
                </p>

                <p
                    class="
                        mt-4
                        text-slate-600
                        leading-8
                    "
                >
                    Users should independently
                    verify all information and
                    consult official government
                    sources before making any
                    passport application decisions.
                </p>

            </div>

            <!-- Updates -->

            <div
                class="
                    bg-gradient-to-r
                    from-blue-50
                    via-white
                    to-indigo-50
                    rounded-3xl
                    border
                    border-blue-100
                    p-10
                "
            >

                <h2
                    class="
                        text-3xl
                        font-bold
                        text-slate-900
                    "
                >
                    Updates To This Policy
                </h2>

                <p
                    class="
                        mt-6
                        text-slate-600
                        leading-8
                    "
                >
                    This Privacy Policy may be
                    updated periodically to reflect
                    improvements, legal requirements
                    or operational changes.
                </p>

                <p
                    class="
                        mt-4
                        text-slate-600
                        leading-8
                    "
                >
                    Continued use of the website
                    indicates acceptance of the
                    latest version of this policy.
                </p>

            </div>

        </section>

        <!-- Footer CTA -->

        <section
            class="
                py-24
                text-center
            "
        >

            <h2
                class="
                    text-4xl
                    font-bold
                    text-slate-900
                "
            >
                Privacy First Verification
            </h2>

            <p
                class="
                    mt-4
                    text-lg
                    text-slate-600
                "
            >
                Review your documents with
                confidence and transparency.
            </p>

            <a
                href="/"
                class="
                    inline-block
                    mt-8
                    px-8
                    py-4
                    rounded-xl
                    bg-blue-600
                    text-white
                    font-semibold
                    hover:bg-blue-700
                    transition
                "
            >
                Back To Verification Tool
            </a>

        </section>

    </main>

</body>

</html>